article.description: — Jamar Brown had 22 points in UMKC's 77-60 win against Oral Roberts in a Summit League opener on Friday night.
article.headline: Brown's 22 points lead UMKC over Oral Roberts 77-60
article.linkText: Brown's 22 points lead UMKC over Oral Roberts 77-60
article.story: KANSAS CITY, Mo. -- — Jamar Brown had 22 points in UMKC's 77-60 win against Oral Roberts in a Summit League opener on Friday night. Brown had 10 rebounds for the Kangaroos (6-8). Melvyn Ebonkoli scored 11 points and Cameron Faas finished with 11 points, while adding seven rebounds. The Golden Eagles (5-7) were led in scoring by Issac McBride, who finished with 21 points. Kareem Thompson added 14 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
